'desc': [u'

Span Women's Leggings Price: Rs.699

A collection of leggings is a must-have in every woman’s wardrobe to mix and match your kurtis and tunics. Span presents this pair of stylish and well-fitted solid green leggings to flaunt your beautiful legs. Crafted from a blend of lycra
column17:
this pair of Span Leggings with patch pockets at the back gives you a stylish and chic look. The panel and stitch detailing make these leggings look exclusively unique and fashionable.

Slip into these vibrant coloured Span Leggings for a casual outing during the weekend by teaming them with a matching kurta or a tunic. A pair of embellished or heeled sandals gels well with this quirky casual outfit.
